that a son of mine,

323
00:18:14,611 --> 00:18:18,012
a Jackson, wants to go
to some jerk agricultural college

324
00:18:18,115 --> 00:18:19,980
and study to be a horse doctor?

325
00:18:20,984 --> 00:18:23,612
