Oh, you're just imagining things.

338
00:19:07,030 --> 00:19:10,966
Every boy has certain disagreements
with his father. That's natural.

339
00:19:11,067 --> 00:19:12,591
All the time? Is that natural?

340
00:19:12,702 --> 00:19:16,536
